org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.cpp.cdt.texteditor.editor

Class DelegatingSourceViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.cpp.cdt.texteditor.editor.DelegatingSourceViewer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jface.text.ITextViewer, org.eclipse.jface.text.source.ISourceViewer
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class DelegatingSourceViewer
extends Object
implements org.eclipse.jface.text.source.ISourceViewer
    Unsuccessful attempt to create a delegating source viewer that changes the implementation of the operation getSelectionProvider of a source viewer. This does not work in case of CDT since the source viewer is cast to CSourceViewer later. CURRENTLY NOT USED

    • Field Summary

      • Fields inherited from interface org.eclipse.jface.text.source.ISourceViewer
